Misspelling, the correct name is Lapeyrère.
&quot;Augustin Manuel Hubert Gaston Boué de Lapeyrère (18 January 1852 - 17 February 1924) was a French admiral during World War I. He was a strong proponent of naval reform, and is comparable to Admiral Jackie Fisher of the British Royal Navy.&quot;
